# =============================================================================
# KDX Monorepo - 统一 Git 忽略规则
# 涵盖技术栈: Python/Django/FastAPI + Node.js/Vue + Docker
# =============================================================================

# ============================================
# 通用 IDE 和编辑器
# ============================================
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
# ============================================
# Python (Django/FastAPI 后端)
# ============================================
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so

# Distribution / packaging
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
share/python-wheels/
